name: Rhythm and Lead
description: This is my 5th piece and the first that I think is okay. It celebrates my passion for music and guitars as well as a throwback to my youth when legos is all I wanted to play with. The goal is to stimulate youthful fun while admiring the legend that these instruments represent. All 4 voxel creations are icons. Achieving minimalism and recognizability is the goal. File is an .mp4 at 4k resolution. Also congrats to the 7 who supported my first mints. This NFT community is amazing. Rock on!
